Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:05.45,cn-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be35}{\t(\fscx115)}{\org(-5000,436)\frz-0.1\t(0,250,\frz0)\t(350,850)}一二三四
