Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:20.05,cn-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be35}{\t(\fscx115)}{\org(-5000,436)\frz-0.1\t(0,250,\frz0)\t(350,850)}从何处开始是清晨
